data.description:
CITY WATER! High and Dry! Needs little clearing or fill since a home was once there! BUILDABLE LAND IN A SUPER LOCATION! ONLY 2 lots left on Natal! Close to all the brand new NW Palm Bay neighborhoods, roads & sidewalks. 
Just minutes from the St. John's stick marsh with air boating and fishing galore! Or to Heritage High School and the Heritage Pkwy. Then it's 192 east will take you to the beaches or west will bring you to Orlando! This spot can't be beat! 
***The BEST part is no HOA!***
